<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Good afternoon, Abig=
ail &amp; All,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></s=
pan></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><u><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Re: C90306048 - Fi=
re at 23 Mays Street, Devonport [WW-ACTIVE.FID3167762] &nbsp;<o:p></o:p></sp=
an></u></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></s=
pan></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Please find attached=
 the following documents included in the tender review for Tower Claim# C903=
06048:<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></s=
pan></p>
<ol start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:4.5pt;mso-list:l1 level1=
 lfo1"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Uncosted scope of work provided to a=
ll tender respondents. A copy of which has already been presented. &nbsp;<o:=
p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:4.5p=
t;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1"><b><i><span lang=3D"FR" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt=
">Asset Managers</span></i></b><span lang=3D"FR" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">=
 tender response [Column O =E2=80=93 Tender comparison]<o:p></o:p></span></l=
i><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:4.5pt;mso-list:l1 leve=
l1 lfo1"><b><i><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Arc Projects</span></i></b><=
span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"> tender response [Column M =E2=80=93 Tender c=
omparison]
<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:4=
.5pt;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1"><b><i><span lang=3D"PT-BR" style=3D"font-size:=
11.0pt">JLG</span></i></b><span lang=3D"PT-BR" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"> t=
ender response [Column K =E2=80=93 Tender comparison]<o:p></o:p></span></li>=
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:4.5pt;mso-list:l1 level1=
 lfo1"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Comparative summary spreadsheet incl=
uding ASURNZ cost estimate. [Column I =E2=80=93 Tender comparison]<o:p></o:p=
></span></li></ol>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">All tenders are comp=
lete and have accounted for all items detailed on the uncosted scope of work=
s provided by ASURNZ.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">In the comparative s=
ummary you will see that I have presented some line items in blue. This is t=
o indicate where the tenderer has provided a PC sum for this item.<o:p></o:p=
></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Any questions which y=
ou may have in relation to any of the specific items in the tender compariso=
n, please do not hesitate to ask.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Our recommendation i=
s to settle the structural claim based on the most competitive tender respon=
se provided by JLG. $419,434.08 Incl GST.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I look forward to fu=
rther correspondence and receiving the findings from your independent consul=
tants in due course.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Best Regards,<o:p></=
o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Grant. &nbsp;<o:p></=
o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<o=
