<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-NZ"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Hi Stephen,<o:p></o:=
p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Below is a copy of a=
n email which I sent to all parties this afternoon outlaying the expected ti=
me frames of the results which will be available to be shared with all regar=
ding test results from 23 Mays Street,
 Devonport.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></s=
pan></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Prior to receiving t=
he report from the forensic testing =E2=80=93 I am keen to take whatever ste=
ps I can to progress the claim.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Preliminary results a=
nd findings suggest that we may have a relatively complete understanding of w=
hat the final scope of works will be to fully remediate the property under t=
he claim.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></s=
pan></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">If we accept on a pr=
eliminary basis that the scope of works required to remediate the property i=
s
<b><u>generally defined</u></b> as follows:<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></s=
pan></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><u><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Basement Level</s=
pan></u><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<ul type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l2 level1 lfo4"><span style=
=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Clean and decontaminate all exposed internal brick sur=
faces to ground level of dwelling<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoList=
Paragraph" style=3D"mso-list:l2 level1 lfo4"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt=
">Replace charred timber framework to midfloor structure and ground floor wa=
lls as required<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D=
"mso-list:l2 level1 lfo4"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Rebuild rear deck=
 and steps to match existing
<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l2 l=
evel1 lfo4"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Replace all hardwood decking bo=
ards to internal balcony
<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l2 l=
evel1 lfo4"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Clean and encapsulate all timbe=
r structural components to ground-floor walls and midfloor structure as requ=
ired<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:=
l2 level1 lfo4"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Replace midfloor insulation=
<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l2 l=
evel1 lfo4"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Replace ceiling linings to grou=
nd floor as required<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" st=
yle=3D"mso-list:l2 level1 lfo4"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Supply and i=
nstall rear pedestrian door to rear of ground floor<o:p></o:p></span></li><l=
i class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l2 level1 lfo4"><span style=3D=
"font-size:11.0pt">Clean and repaint bi-folding basement doors to ground flo=
or<o:p></o:p></span></li></ul>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><u><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Second Level<o:p>=
</o:p></span></u></p>
<ul type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l16 level1 lfo5"><span styl=
e=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Disconnect, clean, and reinstall existing electrical o=
utlets and fittings as required<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListPa=
ragraph" style=3D"mso-list:l16 level1 lfo5"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"=
>Remove all gib-board linings from the interior of the dwelling =E2=80=93
<u>exterior walls only [?]</u>. Ceilings to remain<o:p></o:p></span></li><li=
 class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l16 level1 lfo5"><span style=3D=
"font-size:11.0pt">Clean and decontaminate all interior brick surfaces in th=
e exterior wall cavities<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph=
" style=3D"mso-list:l16 level1 lfo5"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Encaps=
ulate all timber framing to all exposed walls<o:p></o:p></span></li><li clas=
s=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l16 level1 lfo5"><span style=3D"fon=
t-size:11.0pt">Re-line all exposed walls with new gib-board wall linings. Gi=
b-stop and sand to L4<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" s=
tyle=3D"mso-list:l16 level1 lfo5"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Seal and a=
pply 2 topcoats to all new plasterboard linings<o:p></o:p></span></li><li cl=
ass=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l16 level1 lfo5"><span style=3D"f=
ont-size:11.0pt">Clean and repaint all remaining interior surfaces. Internal=
 doors, exterior joinery, wardrobes, etc<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"=
MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l16 level1 lfo5"><span style=3D"font-siz=
e:11.0pt">Remove kitchen cabinetry as required to clean and decontaminate an=
y adjoining wall surfaces<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagrap=
h" style=3D"mso-list:l16 level1 lfo5"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Strip=
 and refit entire bathroom to allow for decontamination and remediation as r=
equired. Reuse existing fitting and fixtures where possible<o:p></o:p></span=
></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l16 level1 lfo5"><spa=
n style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Clean polished hardwood strip flooring [ no re-=
coat of polyurethane ]<o:p></o:p></span></li></ul>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><u><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Roof Space</span>=
</u><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<ul type=3D"disc">
