l1 lfo6">
<span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Remove and replace all existing roof insula=
tion<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-le=
ft:-4.5pt;mso-list:l13 level1 lfo6">
<span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Encapsulate all timber roof structure frami=
ng.<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-lef=
t:-4.5pt;mso-list:l13 level1 lfo6">
<span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Remove and replace roofing underlay paper<o=
