pan></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I will need to discu=
ss the above with you in some detail, accepting that you may make correction=
s as required =E2=80=93 however once we have discussed the
<b><i><u>draft proposed scope</u></i></b> I will request that you provide To=
wer Insurance with a draft copy of the scope at which we arrive, and an acco=
mpanying cost estimate for reserving and quoting purposes.<o:p></o:p></span>=
</p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Let=E2=80=99s talk t=
omorrow when we can.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Many Thanks,<o:p></o=
:p></span></p>
