<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Good afternoon Raffa=
ella &amp; All,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I have just spoken w=
ith Abigail Collin re the forthcoming test results.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">We expect the test r=
esults to be available to share with all parties by the end of next week. I h=
ave chased the provider to expedite this.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">The preliminary repo=
rt from the Forensic Testing will contain the =E2=80=98raw data=E2=80=99 fro=
m the laboratory results, and the locations of the sample sites from where t=
he tests were conducted.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">As promised this pre=
liminary report will be shared with all as soon as it is received and it wil=
l be followed by a fuller report which will provide Towers position on the f=
indings of the report.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
